<i>he was waiting inside!</i>

145
00:07:27,865 --> 00:07:29,332
I'm staying forever.

146
00:07:29,367 --> 00:07:30,834
You're all stuck
with that.

147
00:07:30,868 --> 00:07:33,803
'Cause I'm your new daddy,
the Fat in the...

148
