I'm frightened of nothing,
not even hellfires.

150
00:07:41,545 --> 00:07:45,281
Just don't let me ever be played
by Mike Myers.

151
00:07:45,316 --> 00:07:46,516
(groans)

152
00:07:48,619 --> 00:07:52,622
