208
00:10:25,136 --> 00:10:28,071
So, in conclusion,
my show-and-tell is...

209
00:10:28,105 --> 00:10:29,573
this!

210
00:10:29,607 --> 00:10:32,642
Excellent, Lisa.
A-plus.

211
00:10:32,677 --> 00:10:34,044
Bart, your turn.

212
00:10:34,078 --> 00:10:37,881
Well, my show-and-tell is
that I'm on Lisa's body.

213
00:10:37,915 --> 00:10:39,549
