410
00:17:40,932 --> 00:17:43,400
But how do I get my hands on it?

411
00:17:43,434 --> 00:17:45,001
Oh, I'm an idiot!

412
00:17:45,036 --> 00:17:46,002
Of course!

413
00:17:46,037 --> 00:17:47,370
I get Marge to marry Moe,

414
00:17:47,405 --> 00:17:48,472
